This product includes constant lattice/codebook tables vendored from llama.cpp
(the ggml library), used by the GGUF IQ1/IQ2/IQ3 grid-codebook dequantizers in
src/ModelSharp/Weights/GgufIqGrids.cs.

  Project:  llama.cpp / ggml
  Source:   https://github.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp
  File:     ggml/src/ggml-common.h
  Commit:   050ee92d04c2e1f639025786dea701c70e7d4204
  URL:      https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ggml-org/llama.cpp/050ee92d04c2e1f639025786dea701c70e7d4204/ggml/src/ggml-common.h
  License:  MIT

The following tables are transcribed verbatim: iq2xxs_grid, iq2xs_grid,
iq2s_grid, iq3xxs_grid, iq3s_grid, iq1s_grid, kmask_iq2xs, ksigns_iq2xs. The
dequantization algorithms in src/ModelSharp/Weights/GgufDequant.cs are ported
from the corresponding dequantize_row_iq* routines in ggml/src/ggml-quants.c at
the same commit.

